@masterplusmargarita PLAY. THIS. GAME.

Now, this is just my humble opinion here. But to me, this is the only RPG that could ever compete with Chrono Trigger when it comes to truly heart-felt and wonderfully up-lifting adventure. It's one of the 5th best JRPGs of all time, and there's no comparison to any other on the list, really. You can tell the game was made by a woman, unlike the macho Final Fantasies and inbred Tales games.

It's worth the hassle.
